"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-team-gb-boxer-makes-heartbreaking-statement-controversial-olympics-defeat-21322460\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB boxer Delicious Orie felt he 'let everybody down' after suffering a controversial defeat at the ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.6557904484073978, \"rank\": 0.46403704674471424, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old, who wasinspired by former Olympic champion and heavyweight champion Anthony Joshua, was expected to challenge for a medal after impressive at amateur level.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie celebrated gold medal success at the 2022Commonwealth Gamesshortly after resolving his citizenship status to get a British passport, before winning the European Games in 2023.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British passport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those results ensured Orie entered the Paris Games as the No.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2 seed but his participation at the Olympics ended prematurely courtesy of a split-decision defeat to Armenia's Davit Chaloyan.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9993951298803305, \"rank\": 0.0006052273939592131, \"text\": \"Armenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie dominated the first round before Chaloyan came back into the fight late on and progressed at the expense of the Team GB medal prospect.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have let everybody down, I have let Great Britain down, I am really upset,' an emotional Orie said.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9941732703357656, \"rank\": 0.005668165183750593, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just have to lick my wounds and carry on I guess.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think I did just enough to win, but you can make an argument for Chaloyan I guess, but I need to watch it back.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He was a little bit busier in the third round, he scored the more eye-catching shots, the ones I should not have let through my guard but it happened.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The escalation has been great but unfortunately it's come to a hard stop in my amateur career, it's something I am going to have to hold for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'At the moment I feel like it's breaking me but in a few years I can be a mature enough individual to look back and think I gave it my all.'\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked whether he felt extra pressure after Team GB's poor start to the boxing in Paris, Orie added: 'I guess I have been under a bit of pressure but that wasn't the reason for what happened today.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.6557904484073978, \"rank\": 0.46403704674471424, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996116458, \"rank\": 3.883035937953206e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's all over for Delicious Orie at#Paris2024\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00a9Armenia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Davit Chaloyan gets the win by split decision.#BBCOlympics#Olympicspic.twitter.com/NUau9Vkqh1  'I just let a few stupid shots in that I should not have and that was it.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a good level but I should be beating that type of level to achieve the things if I want to achieve.'\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie's shock defeat proved controversial on social media, with several fans of the opinion that he did enough to take the victory.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Popular boxing YouTube channelIFL TV posted on X: 'Delicious Orie has just been robbed against Davit Chaloyan.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2224, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999872281288639, \"rank\": 1.2772034352950056e-05, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's an absolute disgrace.'\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie's controversial defeat comes after fellowTeam GB boxer Rosie Eccles was left in tears after another contentious loss in Paris.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.998735102495517, \"rank\": 0.0012662934935884357, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"score\": 0.8123391352577319, \"rank\": 0.23071087057566636, \"text\": \"Rosie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"score\": 0.999614505601109, \"rank\": 0.00032379211931034637, \"text\": \"Eccles\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\"}, {\"begin\": 2476, \"end\": 2481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996116458, \"rank\": 3.883035937953206e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision led to boos in the stadium and a tearful Eccles later said: 'I knew I'd won the fight.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really, really shocked.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'In my mind I won that fight.\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know what to say other than I am really grateful for everyone that helped me get here.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I appreciate you all and I am sorry I could not get it over the line.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knew she was a tricky opponent, but I felt I did the job.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed disciplined and kept to my game and I thought I had done enough.\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have devoted my whole life for an Olympic medal but unfortunately for me, and Charley as well yesterday, it wasn't to be.'\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BBC boxing pundit Steve Bunce was among those stunned by the decision, saying: 'I am genuinely shocked.\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Bunce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Bunce\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Bunce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Bunce\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I really did think she'd [Rosie Eccles] get it.\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a brutal outcome.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got independent judges here.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They went with the one who got deducted a point and she actually fouled.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The two judges who had it even voted for the woman who had an infringement.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really annoyed.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a bad decision.'\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics star breaks world record in Paris - but it will not count  ArrowMORE:Team GB star and BBC commentator convinced he was wrongly denied gold medal at Olympics  ArrowMORE:Tom Daley proudly gives new Olympics diving partner Noah Williams X-rated gift  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3534, \"end\": 3539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996116458, \"rank\": 3.883035937953206e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5572696637003426e-31, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 3726, \"end\": 3739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 3740, \"end\": 3747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X_rating\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"X-rated\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X_rating\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X_rating\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3997, \"entities\": []}, {\"senten